The Hospital Management System is a console-based Java application designed to manage basic hospital operations such as patient management, doctor listing, and appointment booking.
The system uses JDBC (Java Database Connectivity) to interact with a MySQL database, ensuring reliable storage and retrieval of hospital records.
This project is ideal for academic mini-projects, backend practice, and understanding real-world database-driven Java applications.

